0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <strong>，找到</strong><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的最优策略<strong>实际上是求解线性程序。</strong>或者，换句话来说， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong>的梯度</strong><strong>是多胞形 中的线性函数</strong>。</p><p>我们可以将其形象化如下： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:34.95%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/snaejifege3vekp95ioz" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/cwj6aofwyp50mhzxk4sc 130w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/hmnhzynbvixqwknqhwyo 260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/gsxxpllel5wrhrstkwrn 390w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/anlcdcz8x1limpkzfgzl 520w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/odeqdfgmecaxmlwwppsi 650w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/iojl3nhv2p6b06cjojfn 780w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/Eu6CvP7c7ivcGM3PJ/tswmlhmht6wbebkw5xii 910w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/