pan></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> calculations per second, and he comments that this might be a high estimate.</p></div></li><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fnx0ps7qqw5q9"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnrefx0ps7qqw5q9">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p> So basically, I think it is likely that AGIT(Top 10 computer in 2023, 1 year, 60 petaflops, 1000 TiB) = True.</p></div></li><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fnob9an78pbkp"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnrefob9an78pbkp">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p> Mentioned in the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Codd%27s_cellular_automaton">wikipedia article</a> and see <a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/golly/code/ci/master/tree/Patterns/Self-Rep/Devore/Devore-body.rle">https://sourceforge.net/p/golly/code/ci/master/tree/Patterns/Self-Rep/Devore/Devore-body.rle</a> for the code.</p></div></li><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fnfuqqjhtkkfd"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnreffuqqjhtkkfd">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drosophila_connectome">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drosophila_connectome</a> and <a href="https://flywire.ai/">https://flywire.ai/</a></p></div></li><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fnt3nv8x4807"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnreft3nv8x4807">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p> LaMDA: Language Models for Dialog Applications, section 10 <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2201.08239">https://arxiv.org/abs/2201.08239</a></p></div></li><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fne1cu9j87dlu"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnrefe1cu9j87dlu">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p> Basically, LLMs are showing signs of gen